{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n<body><p>更新時間：11:05 2026-04-27 HKT<br/>發佈時間：11:05 2026-04-27 HKT</p>\n<p>發佈時間：11:05 2026-04-27 HKT</p><p>今（27日）早上9時42分，沙田水泉澳邨街市內，警方接報指一名男子持刀，斬傷兩人，其中一人頸部中刀浴血，另一人的手及臉傷。警員接報到場制服兇徒及將他拘捕，兩名傷者清醒送院治理。警方正調查事件。</p><img alt=\"疑犯被制服拘捕。街坊提供\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9c713e15a87a25e0298cc35e13a3771e/2026-04/679836035_1420707833404823_3711720640289636041_n.jpg\"/><img alt=\"傷者送院。古偉冰及區子安區議員提供\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2ce7e4274bfd04712bc1fa48470f8c09/2026-04/681092261_1420707896738150_1100187527876691214_n.jpg\"/><img alt=\"警員到場調查。古偉冰及區子安區議員提供\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ffb409b1cb8317ed8229257d8addb1d1/2026-04/681231735_1420708043404802_5304662732649582312_n.jpg\"/><img alt=\"其中一名傷者頸部受傷。古偉冰及區子安區議員提供\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/eb19d81ee91184daecf57d294b873057/2026-04/681296755_1420707760071497_5965091045455288362_n.jpg\"/><img alt=\"探員到場調查。梁國峰攝\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1b2a4da93cbce578514303cc20b6175a/2026-04/KakaoTalk_20260427_114817388.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6195d1407b5c6273df3315963aa6b648/2026-04/KakaoTalk_20260427_114852796_02.jpg\"/><img alt=\"警方封鎖現場調查。梁國峰攝\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/731d6303abcb1e9757feb72f11320829/2026-04/KakaoTalk_20260427_114852796_04.jpg\"/><img alt=\"街市內遺下多灘血迹。梁國峰攝\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a1b81d7de703e4cf5362b5d579358a6f/2026-04/KakaoTalk_20260427_114852796_05.jpg\"/><img alt=\"街市地面遺下一對水靴。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/829a747a8826c44533d05927ec325338/2026-04/KakaoTalk_20260427_114852796_08.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d36106cdd0617923a08653fb7101b583/2026-04/KakaoTalk_20260427_114852796_09.jpg\"/><p>現場消息稱，涉事者為水泉澳街市的檔販，據了解，魚檔檔販向豬肉檔檔販施襲，現場遺下多灘血迹、疑為魚檔檔販的一對水靴、一對相信為傷者的膠拖鞋。</p><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3f3d5135731ce40bcf9ef81514165333/2026-04/KakaoTalk_20260427_115136560.jpg\"/><img alt=\"大批警員在街市調查。梁國峰攝\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/be2e3ff77c477364b340989983ad9d1f/2026-04/KakaoTalk_20260427_115136560_01.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9ab7f398c56e40eae5cdbd064c556adf/2026-04/KakaoTalk_20260427_115136560_02.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c342029bc0aee657294c40d8594bd41f/2026-04/KakaoTalk_20260427_115136560_03.jpg\"/><img alt=\"現場遺下膠拖鞋。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cd931854c8c7fd4fc8f2c078ab0d1508/2026-04/KakaoTalk_20260427_115136560_04.jpg\"/><img alt=\"探員到場調查。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ac22298f80eeace8b3e14d83285ef760/2026-04/KakaoTalk_20260427_115136560_05.jpg\"/><p>最Hit</p>\n</body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-27T05:25:52.319327+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":249,"images":16,"source":"星島頭條","fallback":"none"}}